node.text:
Happy Friday #FitFam 💪🏼
I will be live April 19th @ 7:45pm for a home body workout.
Wanna join?
💥 Download @onthego_fit FIT APP (link in bio) and sign up for my live class; you can also view and select 1:1 training session dates!
We are all in this together —let’s keep grinding! ☑️
🎥 @lee_lhgfx @alexcurson

📱iPhone 12 + PS5 + MacBook + Apple Watch + Make up or CASH 💵 
It’s easy to enter, just follow these steps:

1. Follow the profile @giftsdaanalu and ALL accounts they following 

2. Like this official photo.

3. Follow : 
@shaiden
@hardbodysupplementsbrand @imlawpayne

🚨 Your profile must be public on the day of the draw.

You cannot tag fake accounts, fan clubs, companies, celebrities. 

💋GOOD LUCK 🍀
- Winner will be announced on @growupassessoria profile on  August, 31th at 10pm.

📍Winner is responsible for shipping cost.
